{"parse": {"title": "Shaitan", "pageid": 4764, "text": {"*": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"eraicon filtericon\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2020\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2020\"><img alt=\"2020Icon\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"27\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"2020Icon.png\" data-image-key=\"2020Icon.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/0/08/2020Icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/80?cb=20241220224702\" /></a></span><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_RED\" title=\"Cyberpunk RED\"><img alt=\"RedIcon\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"27\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"RedIcon.png\" data-image-key=\"RedIcon.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/4/4d/RedIcon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/80?cb=20210907221400\" /></a></span><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\"><img alt=\"2077Icon\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"20\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"2077Icon.png\" data-image-key=\"2077Icon.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/7/77/2077Icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/80?cb=20180612180205\" /></a></span></div>\n<p>\n<aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-wikia pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"title\">Shaitan</h2>\n\n\t<div class=\"pi-image-collection wds-tabber\" data-source=\"image\">\n\t\t<div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"wds-tabs\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFlashback\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tRED\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t2020\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\">\n\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/8e/Char_profile_shaitan.png/revision/latest?cb=20210114095320\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"Flashback\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/8e/Char_profile_shaitan.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20210114095320\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/8e/Char_profile_shaitan.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20210114095320 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/8e/Char_profile_shaitan.png/revision/latest?cb=20210114095320 2x\" data-relevant=\"1\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" alt=\"Flashback\" width=\"270\" height=\"438\" data-image-key=\"Char profile shaitan.png\" data-image-name=\"Char profile shaitan.png\" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wds-tab__content\">\n\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/0/0d/Shaitan_REDIR4.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20250917033823\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"RED\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/0/0d/Shaitan_REDIR4.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20250917033823\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/0/0d/Shaitan_REDIR4.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20250917033823 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/0/0d/Shaitan_REDIR4.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20250917033823 2x\" data-relevant=\"1\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" alt=\"RED\" width=\"270\" height=\"331\" data-image-key=\"Shaitan REDIR4.jpg\" data-image-name=\"Shaitan REDIR4.jpg\" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wds-tab__content\">\n\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/7/7c/Shaitan_2020SOF2.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240803132648\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"2020\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/7/7c/Shaitan_2020SOF2.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20240803132648\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/7/7c/Shaitan_2020SOF2.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20240803132648 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/7/7c/Shaitan_2020SOF2.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240803132648 2x\" data-relevant=\"1\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" alt=\"2020\" width=\"266\" height=\"500\" data-image-key=\"Shaitan 2020SOF2.jpg\" data-image-name=\"Shaitan 2020SOF2.jpg\" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t</div>\n\n\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Biographical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"status\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Status</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Alive (2045)</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"home\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Home</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pacific_Rim\" title=\"Pacific Rim\">Pacific Rim</a> (2045)</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Physical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"gender\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Gender</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Male</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"cyberware\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Cyberware</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"#Stats_&amp;_Equipment\">See Cyberware</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"equipment\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Equipment</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"#Stats_&amp;_Equipment\">See Equipment</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Faction Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"occupation\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Occupation</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Mercenary\" title=\"Mercenary\">Mercenary</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"role\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Role</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Solo\" title=\"Solo\">Solo</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color pi-collapse pi-collapse-closed\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Appearances</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"appears_games\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Game(s)</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2020\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2020\">Cyberpunk 2020</a></i><br /><i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_RED\" title=\"Cyberpunk RED\">Cyberpunk RED</a></i><br /><i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\">Cyberpunk 2077</a></i></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"appears_books\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Literature</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/Solo_of_Fortune_2\" title=\"Solo of Fortune 2\">Solo of Fortune 2</a></i><br /><i><a href=\"/wiki/Firestorm_Shockwave\" title=\"Firestorm Shockwave\">Firestorm Shockwave</a></i><br /><i><a href=\"/wiki/Interface_RED_Vol._4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Interface RED Vol. 4\">Interface RED Vol. 4</a></i></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Shaitan</b> is a character featured in the <i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_Series\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cyberpunk Series\">Cyberpunk</a></i> universe.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Biography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Biography</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2010s_-_2023\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010s - 2023</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2023_-_2040s\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2023 - 2040s</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Stats_&amp;_Equipment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Stats &amp; Equipment</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Cyberpunk_2020\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cyberpunk 2020</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Biography\">Biography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShaitan%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010s_-_2023\">2010s - 2023</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShaitan%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During the mid-<a href=\"/wiki/2010\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"2010\">2010s</a>, Shaitan was known as a full <a href=\"/wiki/Borg\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Borg\">borg</a> black-ops specialist and anti-corporate type with a special hatred for <a href=\"/wiki/Arasaka\" title=\"Arasaka\">Arasaka</a>. His obsession knew no bounds, as he had decided the corporation's destruction was a paramount objective of his. When working as a <a href=\"/wiki/Mercenary\" title=\"Mercenary\">mercenary</a>, even though Shaitan was willing to accept any job that he could get away with, it always had to be against Arasaka in some way on form, and it had to have serious collateral damage possibilities too. He was also known for occasionally creating or modifying gigs just so he could destroy the corporation's property. Shaitan never used Arasaka products, and was adamant in not working with those that had ties to them. Even during his free time, he spent it trashing Arasaka stuff.\n</p><p>Despite this quirk of his, by the late 2010s, Shaitan's reputation had gone from a good <a href=\"/wiki/Solo\" title=\"Solo\">solo</a> with a reasonable notoriety, to a great one with a phenomenal success record. This was simply due to the fact that anyone else would have been laughed at by this single-handed crusade, but in Shaitan's case, he had somehow managed to elude capture and successfully accomplish objectives for over three years. Shaitan had honed his mind and rebuilt his body for this task only, and he was so good at it that by <a href=\"/wiki/2020\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"2020\">2020</a> he was considered the seventh best solo in North America by the <i>Solo of Fortune</i> magazine. All this fame made people curious about Shaitan's reasonings on his crusade against Arasaka, prompting some speculations, though it was rumored that Shaitan's mother (or another close female relative) was once violated by a member of the Arasaka family, with fingers pointing to <a href=\"/wiki/Saburo_Arasaka\" title=\"Saburo Arasaka\">Saburo Arasaka</a> himself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2020SOF2_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2020SOF2-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p><p>In August of <a href=\"/wiki/2023\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"2023\">2023</a>, Shaitan joined the team that infiltrated the <a href=\"/wiki/Arasaka_Towers\" title=\"Arasaka Towers\">Arasaka Towers</a> after getting a call from <a href=\"/wiki/Johnny_Silverhand\" title=\"Johnny Silverhand\">Johnny Silverhand</a>. They was ambushed by <a href=\"/wiki/Adam_Smasher\" title=\"Adam Smasher\">Adam Smasher</a> and a large number of Arasaka soldiers, though after <a href=\"/wiki/Johnny_Silverhand\" title=\"Johnny Silverhand\">Johnny Silverhand</a>'s death, Shaitan used that opportunity to pin down Smasher in order to provide an escape for the rest team. He was critically wounded by Adam, but still managed to survive the nuke that <a href=\"/wiki/Night_City_Holocaust\" title=\"Night City Holocaust\">went off</a>.\n</p><p>Following the fall of the Arasaka Towers, Shaitan \u2014 in a new FBC \u2014 helped <a href=\"/wiki/Rogue_Amendiares\" title=\"Rogue Amendiares\">Rogue</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Spider_Murphy\" title=\"Spider Murphy\">Spider</a> locate <a href=\"/wiki/Kei_Arasaka\" title=\"Kei Arasaka\">Kei Arasaka</a> aboard the <span class=\"new\" title=\"Sea Viper (page does not exist)\" data-uncrawlable-url=\"L3dpa2kvU2VhX1ZpcGVyP2FjdGlvbj1lZGl0JnJlZGxpbms9MQ==\">Sea Viper</span> after his escape from Night City, which was cruising across the Pacific Ocean. Once the ship was secured, Murphy fulfilled her promise to avenge her friends by soulkilling Kei. Afterwards, Shaitan and the rest of the team returned to North America.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2020FS2_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2020FS2-2\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>2<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-REDINT4_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-REDINT4-3\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>3<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2023_-_2040s\">2023 - 2040s</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShaitan%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Despite the Arasaka Corporation losses in the <a href=\"/wiki/Fourth_Corporate_War\" title=\"Fourth Corporate War\">Fourth Corporate War</a>, their continued existence kept tormenting Shaitan. After hearing of a major Arasaka operation somewhere in the Far East, he recklessly installed tons of cyberware on his new body to prepare for an assault. The rapid increase of chrome, however, started to cloud his mind, though Shaitan's obsession and hatred kept him pushing forward. Nonetheless, he eventually lost consciousness after suffering from <a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpsychosis\" title=\"Cyberpsychosis\">cyberpsychosis</a>.\n</p><p>Following an unspecified amount of time, Shaitan awoke on an autonomous cargo ship in the Pacific Ocean. The vessel, which had been stranded after self-replicating mines had destroyed its rudder, had no one aboard other than the borg. Shaitan couldn't remember how he got there, and was unable to connect to the <a href=\"/wiki/Net\" title=\"Net\">Net</a> nor contact with anybody. After a quick search around, however, he found out that the cargo ship was overflowing with high tech from <a href=\"/wiki/Militech\" title=\"Militech\">Militech</a>. So much so, in fact, that not even a lifetime of merc work would be enough to pay for all of it. At that moment, Shaitan realized that his crusade against Arasaka had amounted for nothing, as everything he had destroyed could be easily replaced or rebuilt. The only thing that counted for him was the death of Saburo's son, Kei. Something the Arasaka emperor would not be able to recover.\n</p><p>After securing rations for his borg body, Shaitan started to tinker with the tech around the cargo hold, as it included unique cyberware and experimental technology he could use to better himself. Shaitan began to cannibalize those items for parts, replacing one piece of his body at a time. From a rebuilt <a href=\"/wiki/Militech_Eclipse_(2020)\" title=\"Militech Eclipse (2020)\">Eclipse FBC</a>, Shaitan took its <a href=\"/wiki/FBC_Chameleon_Coating\" title=\"FBC Chameleon Coating\">Chameleon Coating</a>, though it took him months and seven failed surgeries to install it on his own body, almost losing himself in the process. Finally, he found a crate containing an <a href=\"/wiki/Internal_Linear_Frame_%CE%A9\" title=\"Internal Linear Frame \u03a9\">Internal Linear Frame \u03a9</a> labeled as Nuckelavee, though its installation took Shaitan over the edge, making him lose his consciousness again. The next time he remembered waking up, Shaitan found himself wrapped in a tarp while covered in rust and seawater, but for a moment, the cyberpsychosis he felt was comfortable. It was frightening, but at the same time he felt emotionally numb, as if a <a href=\"/wiki/Pain_Editor_(RED)\" title=\"Pain Editor (RED)\">pain editor</a> had been turned on for his soul. Nevertheless, Shaitan knew if he kept pushing he would fully lose himself, so he built a new faceplate from what remained of the Eclipse FBC to center his mind. While doing so, he remembered the promise he did to his mother's memory, the vow to become whatever it took to achieve his revenge, even if he had to become an evil spirit, a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shayatin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Shayatin\">Shaitan</a>. This time, however, he renewed his vow to gain a new purity of purpose and focus on the future.\n</p><p>Over the following years, Shaitan spent his time doing meditation and training in martial arts. He had lost to <a href=\"/wiki/Adam_Smasher\" title=\"Adam Smasher\">Adam Smasher</a> due to his lack of close-quarter combat prowess, but thanks to the interactive training braindances in the cargo hold, he was able to learn all types of martial art styles. All this made Shaitan realize that all arts were connected; body, mind, spirit and chrome were all equal contributors, and he finally considered himself ready to fight once more.\n</p><p>After many years adrift, Shaitan's cargo ship was discovered by a passing <a href=\"/wiki/Nomad\" title=\"Nomad\">nomad</a> vessel. In exchange for the remaining cargo and the ship, they agreed to help Shaitan reach <a href=\"/wiki/Japan\" title=\"Japan\">Japan</a> and supply him with whatever he would need. The money and favors he gained from that trade allowed Shaitan to establish a network of safehouses on the Asian mainland and all over the <a href=\"/wiki/Pacific_Rim\" title=\"Pacific Rim\">Pacific Rim</a>. Unlike his early years, Shaitan would instead strike against Arasaka from where Saburo would least expect, from within. This time, Shaitan was planning to take from him what he would never be able to recover.<sup id=\"cite_ref-REDINT4_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-REDINT4-3\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>3<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Stats_.26_Equipment\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Stats_&amp;_Equipment\">Stats &amp; Equipment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShaitan%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cyberpunk_2020\">Cyberpunk 2020</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShaitan%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:small;\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"6\">Stats</th><th colspan=\"4\">Source(s): <i><a href=\"/wiki/Solo_of_Fortune_2\" title=\"Solo of Fortune 2\">Solo of Fortune 2</a></i>&#160;(p.60)<br /><i><a href=\"/wiki/Firestorm_Shockwave\" title=\"Firestorm Shockwave\">Firestorm Shockwave</a></i>&#160;(p.143)</th></tr><tr><th style=\"width:10%;\">INT</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">8</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">REF</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">15</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">DEX</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">\u2014</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">TECH</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">8</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">COOL</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">9</td></tr><tr><th style=\"width:10%;\">ATTR</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">N/A</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">LUCK</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">6</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">MA</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">20</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">BODY</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">12</td><th style=\"width:10%;\">EMP</th><td style=\"width:10%; text-align:right;\">9/3/7</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Skills</th><td colspan=\"8\">Combat Sense 9, Aikido 8, Athletics 10, Awareness 10, Basic Tech 8, Cybertech 4, Demolitions 6, Driving 7, Education 4, Tactics 5, First Aid 5, Handgun 9, Heavy Weapons 9, Hide/Evade 9, Intimidate 7, Melee 10, Pilot Boat 4, Pilot Fixed Wing 6, Pilot Vectored Thrust 7, Rifle 10, Shadow/Track 8, Stealth 10, Strength Feat 2, SMG 8, Swimming 6, Weapons Tech 7, Wilderness Survival 6</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Cyberware</th><td colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/wiki/Militech_Eclipse\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Militech Eclipse\">Eclipse Covert Operations FBC</a> (w/ added +2 REF (total of 15), +7 MA (total of 20), Shielding, +5 SP (total of 30 all-around), +10 SDP (total of 30 all-around)), audio w/ (level damper, sound editing), optics (w/ image enhancement, tele-optics), legs (w/ heavy pistol (hidden holster), and MML), arms (w/ digital recorder, techscanner, electronics toolkit, weapons toolkit)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Gear</th><td colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/wiki/United_Armaments_CLAW\" title=\"United Armaments CLAW\">United Armaments CLAW</a> (w/ four clips of mixed of APFSDS and HEAT rounds), <a href=\"/wiki/Militech_%22Cowboy%22_U-55_Grenade_Launcher\" title=\"Militech &quot;Cowboy&quot; U-55 Grenade Launcher\">Militech \"Cowboy\" U-55 Grenade Launcher</a> (w/ 36 rounds of mixed frag and concussion), <a href=\"/wiki/Militech_Arms_Avenger\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Militech Arms Avenger\">Militech Avenger</a> (w/ smart and eight clips)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\">Galler